  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/59b289d8bec408d86669938414dd922d.poster.avif?t=1678177116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/59b289d8bec408d86669938414dd922d.webm?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/59b289d8bec408d86669938414dd922d.mp4?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Story :</strong></h2><br><br>The story takes place 7 years after the almost total destruction of human civilization.<br>Planet earth was ravaged by diseases, famine and wars until the appearance of the Z virus, a consequence of all the factors mentioned above.<br>The Z virus whose name comes from zombie virus spreads widely and quickly in an environment of misfortune and death, it is as if the world was offered to him on a golden platter.<br>The population that had survived the diseases and the wars was now very weakened and faced with a danger that was far superior to them.<br>Shortly after its appearance, the virus transformed the majority of the world's population into zombies. The few remaining commanders then unite in order to save what remains to be saved.<br>It was there that they found you and put you on the Azmodeus project. A few years later, you are now well trained to survive in one of the islands chosen to try to restore civilization.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/8c86985ebc3fc1e3cbe5de01ae413adb.poster.avif?t=1678177116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/8c86985ebc3fc1e3cbe5de01ae413adb.webm?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/8c86985ebc3fc1e3cbe5de01ae413adb.mp4?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features :</strong></h2><br><br>Zombie Survival Game with a focus on realistic survival.<br>Customize your character with weapons and gear.<br>Cut down trees, trade with NPCs, fish, hunt, farm, craft, search for loot, manage animals, and kill zombies.<br>Open World island.<br>Improve your Skills.<br>Restoration and improvement of your survival base.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/f9f168241c51759a94dbd2c8faccb72b.poster.avif?t=1678177116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/f9f168241c51759a94dbd2c8faccb72b.webm?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/f9f168241c51759a94dbd2c8faccb72b.mp4?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/59b289d8bec408d86669938414dd922d.poster.avif?t=1678177116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/59b289d8bec408d86669938414dd922d.webm?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/59b289d8bec408d86669938414dd922d.mp4?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Story :</strong></h2><br><br>The story takes place 7 years after the almost total destruction of human civilization.<br>Planet earth was ravaged by diseases, famine and wars until the appearance of the Z virus, a consequence of all the factors mentioned above.<br>The Z virus whose name comes from zombie virus spreads widely and quickly in an environment of misfortune and death, it is as if the world was offered to him on a golden platter.<br>The population that had survived the diseases and the wars was now very weakened and faced with a danger that was far superior to them.<br>Shortly after its appearance, the virus transformed the majority of the world's population into zombies. The few remaining commanders then unite in order to save what remains to be saved.<br>It was there that they found you and put you on the Azmodeus project. A few years later, you are now well trained to survive in one of the islands chosen to try to restore civilization.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/8c86985ebc3fc1e3cbe5de01ae413adb.poster.avif?t=1678177116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/8c86985ebc3fc1e3cbe5de01ae413adb.webm?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/8c86985ebc3fc1e3cbe5de01ae413adb.mp4?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features :</strong></h2><br><br>Zombie Survival Game with a focus on realistic survival.<br>Customize your character with weapons and gear.<br>Cut down trees, trade with NPCs, fish, hunt, farm, craft, search for loot, manage animals, and kill zombies.<br>Open World island.<br>Improve your Skills.<br>Restoration and improvement of your survival base.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/f9f168241c51759a94dbd2c8faccb72b.poster.avif?t=1678177116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/f9f168241c51759a94dbd2c8faccb72b.webm?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311780/extras/f9f168241c51759a94dbd2c8faccb72b.mp4?t=1678177116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
